 9030(c)","children":[],"tail":") shall be available to cover the cost of additional benefits payable due to section 2112(a) of such Act by reason of the amendments made by subsection (a) [amending this section] as well as to cover the cost of such benefits payable due to such section 2112(a) as in effect on the day before the date of enactment of this Act ["},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2021-03-11"},"text":"Mar. 11, 2021","children":[],"tail":"].”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/260/dN/tII/s234/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–260, div. N, title II, § 234(c)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2020-12-27"},"text":"Dec. 27, 2020","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/134/1959"},"text":"134 Stat. 1959","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/116/260/dN/tII/s234/c"},"text":"“Funds appropriated under section 2112(c) of the CARES Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s9030/c"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 9030(c)","children":[],"tail":") shall be available to cover the cost of additional benefits payable due to section 2112(a) of such Act ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s9030/a"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 9030(a)","children":[],"tail":"] by reason of the amendments made by subsection (a) [amending this section] as well as to cover the cost of such benefits payable due to such section 2112(a) as in effect on the day before the date of enactment of this Act ["},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2020-12-27"},"text":"Dec. 27, 2020","children":[],"tail":"].”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
